<tr><td nowrap width="20%" valign=baseline align=right><b>Notable Features: </b></td><td colspan=4 align=left valign=baseline><a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Flipper">Flippers</a> (2), <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Pop_Bumper">Pop&nbsp;bumper</a> (1), <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Slingshot">Slingshots</a> (2), <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Standup_Target">Standup&nbsp;targets</a> (12), <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Spinning_Target">Spinning&nbsp;target</a> (1), <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Kick-out_Hole">Kick-out&nbsp;hole</a> (1), <a target="glossary" class="glossarylink" href="/glossary.php#Captive_Ball">Captive&nbsp;balls</a> (2).</td></tr>
